Description: The GGZ Gaming Zone Chat Bot
 Grubby is a nice bot which is intended to run on GGZ
 servers. It is highly configurable, extensible with
 plugins, and gets smarter the longer it runs.
 .
 A more serious use is to alert or notify other players,
 or to remember messages for them.
